  recommended to use when manually copying, syncing our mounting the
  repositories. When choosing these locations, it is sufficient to set the
  repository location in &yast; &crow; to <guimenu>Custom</guimenu> without
  having to specify a detailed location for each repository. Refer to <xref
  linkend="sec.depl.adm_conf.repos.scc.alternatives"/> and <xref
  linkend="sec.depl.adm_inst.crowbar.repos"/> for details.
 </para>

